Ajanta Toothbrush’ was found by Mahipal Vijaychand Sariya in 1949 in Bombay. Being amongst the first to manufacture tooth brushes in India, today Ajanta Toothbrush is a well established brand for 60 years since its inception. The brand name has quickly grown on to become one of India’s most recognizable household names with it’s slogan “Ajanta Toothbrush papa ka, mummy ka, bhaiya ka, ...aur Ajanta mera” being widely recognized amongst the population. We are proud of the fact that the name Ajanta is trusted and relied upon by consumers all over the country. A pioneer of toothbrush industry in India, Ajanta has now introduced in its portfolio a variety of other oral care as well as hair care products, all designed to provide excellent value for money.

Soft toothbrush features circular power bristles to help effectively clean teeth. Easy-to-grip handle to provide comfort and control while brushing. Cleaning tip bristles to effectively reach and clean back teeth and between teeth. Helps remove tooth stains
